text: "Overload" is a 2000 debut single by English band Sugababes and is the leading single from their debut studio album One Touch. It went to number 2 in Greece and New Zealand, number 3 in Austria, Germany and Hungary, number 4 in Iceland, number 5 in Switzerland, number 6 in the United Kingdom, number 10 in Scotland, number 12 in Norway and number 15 in Ireland. It was covered by Bastille in 2015. ==Track listings== Notes * denotes additional producer(s) ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Debut singles Category:Sugababes songs Category:Pop songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Sugababes
